msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:120
#: a32af34537c04e99b11c72cdc3b086cf
msgid "Select the option to test this media and install Qubes OS."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:124
#: e3002eee0b404ef288089ac8a3e737ed
msgid ""
"**Note:** If the latest stable release is not compatible with your "
"hardware, you may wish to consider :doc:`testing a newer release </user"
"/downloading-installing-upgrading/testing>`      ."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:126
#: 9802a267a8494645b096fb62191db46d
msgid ""
"If the boot screen does not appear, there are several options to "
"troubleshoot. First, try rebooting your computer. If it still loads your "
"currently installed operating system or does not detect your installation"
" medium, make sure the boot order is set up appropriately. The process to"
" change the boot order varies depending on the currently installed system"
" and the motherboard manufacturer. If **Windows 10** is installed on your"
" machine, you may need to follow specific instructions to change the boot"
" order. This may require an `advanced reboot "
"<https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4026206/windows-10-find-safe-"
"mode-and-other-startup-settings>`__."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:129
#: 7cdb11aa33ac4f05970dee87f9b30a27
msgid "The installer home screen"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:132
#: a61d77448a3d400eb1b018312989dfb0
msgid ""
"On the first screen, you are asked to select the language that will be "
"used during the installation process. When you are done, select "
"**Continue**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:134
#: 09f43912541d4949a377b3acddcb6116
msgid "|welcome|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:363
#: e226d06aeb3e4c18bb40a2c28a4e1a17
