msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:276
#: f3e9b51b29f245ab9077af1900c1e48d
msgid ""
"**Create default system qubes:** These are the core components of the "
"system, required for things like internet access."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:278
#: ee97d8218f8348ebb986f5897446578d
msgid ""
"**Create default application qubes:** These are how you compartmentalize "
"your digital life. There’s nothing special about the ones the installer "
"creates. They’re just suggestions that apply to most people. If you "
"decide you don’t want them, you can always delete them later, and you can"
" always create your own."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:280
#: 137f2c73499f4c059d96c3ac20b7e5f0
msgid ""
"**Create Whonix Gateway and Workstation qubes:** If you want to use "
"Whonix, you should select this option."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:282
#: 0e52c9e8fe984b4baa41a9ab6cf07857
msgid ""
"**Enabling system and template updates over the Tor anonymity network "
"using Whonix:** If you select this option, then whenever you install or "
"update software in dom0 or a template, the internet traffic will go "
"through Tor."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:286
#: 554e4299b7e34479ad23f5470adc112c
msgid ""
"**Create USB qube holding all USB controllers:** Just like the network "
"qube for the network stack, the USB qube isolates the USB controllers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:288
#: 230153bc8b72488aa2a59823234485ec
msgid ""
"**Use sys-net qube for both networking and USB devices:** You should "
"select this option if you rely on a USB device for network access, such "
"as a USB modem or a USB Wi-Fi adapter."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:292
#: 376702fcbd6840cfa315d2b97f3e1861
msgid ""
"**Do not configure anything:** This is for very advanced users only. If "
"you select this option, you’ll have to set everything up manually "
"afterward."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:296
#: 12ec17f17e3343cdb0a5425c026a3d24
msgid ""
"When you’re satisfied with you choices, press **Done**. This "
"configuration process may take a while, depending on the speed and "
