#: a44155c3af3a454e9fb825ed2996a2b9
msgid ""
"Next, :doc:`update </user/how-to-guides/how-to-update>` your installation"
" to ensure you have the latest security updates. Frequently updating is "
"one of the best ways to remain secure against new threats."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:317
#: 5bba0c792f9748b9833cc01fedd4ebbc
msgid "Security"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:320
#: 72f6426db4014c1f8c94a1833ec8faea
msgid ""
"The Qubes OS Project occasionally issues `Qubes Security Bulletins (QSBs)"
" <https://www.qubes-os.org/security/qsb/>`__ as part of the :doc:`Qubes "
"Security Pack (qubes-secpack) </project-security/security-pack>`. It is "
"important to make sure that you receive all QSBs in a timely manner so "
"that you can take action to keep your system secure. (While `updating "
"<#updating>`__ will handle most security needs, there may be cases in "
"which additional action from you is required.) For this reason, we "
"strongly recommend that every Qubes user subscribe to the :ref:`qubes-"
"announce <introduction/support:qubes-announce>` mailing list."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:322
#: dd4a483ac8be4d9f927613389f8b2c3d
msgid ""
"In addition to QSBs, the Qubes OS Project also publishes `Canaries "
"<https://www.qubes-os.org/security/canary/>`__, XSA summaries, template "
"releases and end-of-life notices, and other items of interest to Qubes "
"users. Since these are not essential for all Qubes users to read, they "
"are not sent to :ref:`qubes-announce <introduction/support:qubes-"
"announce>` in order to keep the volume on that list low. However, we "
"expect that most users, especially novice users, will find them helpful. "
"If you are interested in these additional items, we encourage you to "
"subscribe to the `Qubes News RSS feed <https://www.qubes-"
"os.org/feed.xml>`__ or join one of our other :doc:`venues "
"</introduction/support>`, where these news items are also announced."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:324
#: 29414c98dfdf49fba6e474ecd734cd2f
msgid ""
"For more information about Qubes OS Project security, please see the "
":doc:`security center </project-security/security>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:327
#: f2d04824451e4237ba42efa8f6dae16f
msgid "Backups"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide-4.1.rst:330
#: 4726a873f2ae47ec9209eb501e14536c
msgid ""
"It is extremely important to make regular backups so that you don’t lose "
"your data unexpectedly. The :doc:`Qubes backup system </user/how-to-"
"guides/how-to-back-up-restore-and-migrate>` allows you to do this "
"securely and easily."
msgstr ""

